"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-06-paris-2024-olympics-abdul-charges-nigerian-weightlifters-to-compete-firm-fair\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  President of Nigeria Weightlifting Federation, NWF, Ibrahim Abdul has charged lifters participating at the ongoing 2024 Olympic Games in Paris, to compete firmly and fairly.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999999998215117, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigeria Weightlifting Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Weightlifting_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Wildlife_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999998126177336, \"rank\": 1.4329591027272942e-07, \"text\": \"NWF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Wildlife_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Wildlife_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 71, \"end\": 78, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\", \"score\": 0.9306730472343332, \"rank\": 0.0512130807173318, \"text\": \"Ibrahim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_Johor\"}, {\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999042158879, \"rank\": 9.578418376844361e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Nigeria will be represented by two female lifters in Paris.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9847062279286353, \"rank\": 0.015531304290482896, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999042158879, \"rank\": 9.578418376844361e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rafiatu Folashade Lawal will compete in the 59kg class, while Joy \\u1eccgbonne Eze will fight for honours in the 71kg category.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 260, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafiatu_Lawal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafiatu Folashade Lawal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafiatu_Lawal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafiatu_Lawal\"}, {\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"score\": 0.6906757134424053, \"rank\": 0.4478574828560571, \"text\": \"Joy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\"}, {\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eze\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eze\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eze\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eze\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lawal and Eze will be aiming to better Nigeria's weightlifting performance at the Olympics (two medals - a silver and a bronze at the 2000 and 2008 Olympics).\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9847062279286353, \"rank\": 0.015531304290482896, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are happy with what we have done so far as far as this Olympic Games is concerned.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have two athletes representing us, all of them are females.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They withstood the rigour and pressure in the qualifying series to reach their first Olympic Games,\\\" Abdul said at a press conference in Abuja.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.276398166267562e-21, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have come a long way because now they are competing among the world bests.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told them on the phone a few days ago that they should fear no foe.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody is beatable.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today I reinforce that statement and urge them to compete firm and fair.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have done everything from our end to give them the necessary support including conducting doping tests on them regularly while they camped,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weightlifting event at the 2024 Olympic Games will begin on Tuesday (today).\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"EPL: Nicol gives Arsenal one big reason to sign Osimhen  Ballon d'Or 2024: Kroos names player that will not win award this year  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins 